- `d:\NAM_PHUONG_SOFTWARE\DU LIEU MPS\erp-nam-phuong\frontend\src\pages\accounting\CashPaymentListPage.tsx`
- `d:\NAM_PHUONG_SOFTWARE\DU LIEU MPS\erp-nam-phuong\frontend\src\pages\accounting\AccountingHubPage.tsx`
- `d:\NAM_PHUONG_SOFTWARE\DU LIEU MPS\erp-nam-phuong\frontend\src\App.tsx` (lines 421-450 for route pattern)
